State of North Carolina
v.
Michael Ray Trull No. 618P02-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 8, 2016 Mr. Bruce T. Cunningham, Jr., Attorney at Law, Southern Pines, For Trull, Michael Ray Mr. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, Mr. Joseph L. Hyde, Assistant Attorney General, Ms. Roxann L. Vaneekhoven, District Attorney, For State of N.C.

ORDER

Ervin, J.

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 18th of August 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Cabarrus County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 8th of December 2016."
